<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِآيَاتِنَا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ تِسْعٌ:</span> العَصَا، وَاليَدُ، وَالجَرَادُ، وَالقُمَّلُ، وَالضَّفَادِعُ، وَالدَّمُ، وَالطُّوفَانُ، وَالسِّنُونَ، وَنَقْصُ الثَّمَرَاتِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَالِينَ}</span> ... مُتَكَبِّرِينَ مُتَطَاوِلِينَ عَلَى النَّاسِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَابِدُونَ}</span> ... مُتَذَلِّلُونَ مُطِيعُونَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَآوَيْنَاهُمَا}</span> ... جَعَلْنَا لَهُمَا مَاوًى وَمَسْكَنًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَبْوَةٍ}</span> ... مَكَانٍ مُرْتَفِعٍ مِنَ الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَاتِ قَرَارٍ}</span> ... مُسْتَوٍ لِلاِسْتِقْرَارِ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَعِينٍ}</span> ... مَاءٍ جَارٍ ظَاهِرٍ لِلْعُيُونِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُمَّتُكُمْ}</span> ... دِينُكُمْ يَا مَعْشَرَ الأَنْبِيَاءِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُمَّةً وَاحِدَةً}</span> ...<span class="c5"> دِينًا وَاحِدًا هُوَ:</span> الإِسْلَامُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَقَطَّعُوا أَمْرَهُم}</span> ... فَتَفَرَّقَ الأَتْبَاعُ فِي الدِّينِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زُبُرًا}</span> ... شِيَعًا، وَأَحْزَابًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَمْرَتِهِمْ}</span> ... ضَلَالَتِهِمْ، وَجَهْلِهِمْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَتَّى حِينٍ}</span> ... إِلَى وَقْتِ نُزُولِ العَذَابِ بِهِمْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّشْفِقُونَ}</span> ... وَجِلُونَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَجِلَةٌ}</span> ... خَائِفَةٌ مِنْ عَدَمِ القَبُولِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَمْرَةٍ مِّنْ هَذَا}</span> ... ضَلَالٍ عَنْ هَذَا القُرْآنِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>